sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Client
    participant UV as Uvicorn
    participant R as foods.py router
    participant F as Food model
    participant DB as MySQL

    C->>+UV: DELETE /foods/2
    UV->>+R: delete_food(food_id=2, conn=Depends(get_db))

    R->>+F: Food(conn), food.id=2
    R->>F: food.exists()
    F->>+DB: SELECT id FROM foods WHERE id=2
    DB-->>-F: row / None

    alt ไม่พบ
        F-->>R: False
        R-->>C: 404 {success:false, error}
    else พบ
        F-->>-R: True
        R->>+F: food.delete()
        F->>+DB: DELETE FROM foods WHERE id=2
        Note over DB: ON DELETE CASCADE\nลบ recipes.food_id=2 ด้วย
        DB-->>-F: rowcount=1
        F-->>-R: True
        R-->>-UV: {success:true, data:{id:2,...}}
        UV-->>-C: 200 OK
    end
